Variable Listing

Use the table below to identify ADaM variables and the {admiral} functions that derive them.

Missing Variables

If you notice a ADaM variable that is missing, please take a moment to file an issue on GitHub to have it added to the listing.

Deprecated/Superseded

Deprecated and Superseded functions are highlighted according to their statuses in admiral v1.0.1.9007, admiralonco v1.0.0, admiralophtha v1.0.0, and admiralvaccine v0.2.0. If you see a deprecated or superseded function, please file an issue on GitHub for the respective admiral package so the table can be updated.

The links to template examples are the most recent available. To access a template from your installed version of a package, use the admiral::use_ad_template() function.
